sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Team Leader
    participant FE as React<br/>SubscriptionPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>ManageTeamSubscriptionView
    participant Perm as IsTeamLeader
    participant Stripe as Stripe API
    participant Router as TierDatabaseRouter
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Select new team plan, click "Upgrade Team"
    FE->>API: POST /api/subscriptions/manage-team/ {plan: "exclusive"}
    API->>Perm: has_permission(request)
    Perm-->>API: Allowed (Team Leader role)
    API->>Stripe: stripe.PaymentIntent.create(amount * member_count)
    Stripe-->>API: Payment confirmed
    API->>DB: EnvironmentMembership.objects.filter(environment=env)
    DB-->>API: All team members
    loop For each team member
        API->>Router: set_db_for_role("exclusive")
        API->>DB: Migrate user to exclusive_db
        API->>DB: UserSubscription.objects.update(plan="exclusive")
    end
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {new_plan, members_upgraded: count}
    FE-->>U: Display "Team upgraded to Exclusive" confirmation
